<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Response from Quiz-Blog Team</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #157A6E, #1e8e85);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="60" height="60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><pattern id="a" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse" width="60" height="60"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23a)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .header-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #157A6E;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .conversation-thread {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .message-card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .user-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        }

        .admin-response {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8, #c8e6c9);
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
        }

        .message-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .message-icon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .user-message .message-header {
            color: #1565c0;
        }

        .admin-response .message-header {
            color: #2e7d32;
        }

        .message-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .user-message .message-content {
            border-left: 3px solid #2196f3;
            color: #0d47a1;
        }

        .admin-response .message-content {
            border-left: 3px solid #4caf50;
            color: #1b5e20;
        }

        .message-text {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .chat-cta {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #157A6E, #1e8e85);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .chat-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .chat-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .chat-button {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .chat-button:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #157A6E;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .help-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .help-title {
            color: #157A6E;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .help-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .help-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .help-icon {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            color: #157A6E;
        }

        .help-text {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .company-info {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .company-name {
            color: #157A6E;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .company-tagline {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .company-location {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-link {
            color: #1f3fcf;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 8px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-link:hover {
            color: #157A6E;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .separator {
            margin: 0 4px;
            color: #999;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 650px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .header-icon {
                font-size: 50px;
            }

            .message-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .message-icon {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }

            .help-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .help-icon {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-icon">💬</div>
            <h1>We've Responded!</h1>
            <p>Your conversation with Quiz-Blog team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi {{name}},
            </div>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                Great news! We've responded to your inquiry. Here's the complete conversation thread for your reference:
            </p>

            <div class="conversation-thread">
                <div class="message-card user-message">
                    <div class="message-header">
                        <div class="message-icon">💭</div>
                        <div>Your Message</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="message-content">
                        <div class="message-text">{{{question}}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="message-card admin-response">
                    <div class="message-header">
                        <div class="message-icon">✅</div>
                        <div>Our Response</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="message-content">
                        <div class="message-text">{{{answer}}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-cta">
                <div class="chat-title">💬 Continue the Conversation</div>
                <div class="chat-description">
                    Have more questions or need further clarification? Visit your chat page to view the complete conversation and reply directly.
                </div>
                <a href="https://quizblog.rw/contact-chat" class="chat-button">
                    🚀 Open Chat Page
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="help-section">
                <div class="help-title">🎯 How can we help you further?</div>
                
                <div class="help-item">
                    <div class="help-icon">📚</div>
                    <div class="help-text">Explore our extensive library of quizzes and study materials</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="help-item">
                    <div class="help-icon">📝</div>
                    <div class="help-text">Read our latest blog articles for additional insights</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="help-item">
                    <div class="help-icon">💬</div>
                    <div class="help-text">Join our community discussions and connect with other learners</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="help-item">
                    <div class="help-icon">🎓</div>
                    <div class="help-text">Track your learning progress with our personalized dashboard</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #157A6E; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                Thank you for engaging with Quiz-Blog! We're here to support your learning journey 🌟
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="company-info">
                <div class="company-name">Quiz-Blog Rwanda</div>
                <div class="company-tagline">Quizzing & Blogging</div>
                <div class="company-location">📍 Kigali | Rwamagana, Rwanda</div>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/quiz-blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/QuizblogRw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/QuizblogRw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/quizblogrw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Website</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=250780579067" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">📱 WhatsApp</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>